{
  "stem": "25589.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We did a lot of reading.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But to put your brains to learning-- I couldn't make myself to do this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I have no explanation for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Maybe a psychiatrist [LAUGHS] or whatever-- has an explanation for that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we couldn't get ourselves to do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At least, I don't remember that anybody-- any of us did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We used to talk to each other about nice things-- what we're going to do if we go out, and the nice things that we used to do-- that type of thing we used to keep ourselves amused with.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what I'm saying?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to keep ourselves amused.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you would get-- if you would start-- yourself thinking about work, we would get almost depressed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we couldn't do it outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have-- why would we have to do it here?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With pleasant things, you don't think-- you think about something nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So therefore, it will be easy to keep your brain happy with something nice, than something learning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe it sounds strange, but that's the way I remembered it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the way I remembered it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's also a very good question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm 16.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I was a fast learner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you're talking about something-- and I would look-- girls.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm not interested in boys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I'm interested in girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was some nice girls passing by.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I says, one of these-- when I come out, I'm going to make up for lost time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But that's one thing, I kept myself going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I come out, I'm going to go back to play soccer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My dream was playing for the-- the Dutch national team.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was my dream.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It never came true.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I played, but I never played for the national team.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
